# Intrinsic design tokens

**Repo:** `intrinsicvalue-llc/design` (submodule at `design/` in product repos)  
**Regenerate:** `npm run build` in design repo  
**Consumption:** `docs/CONSUMPTION.md`

## iOS (SwiftUI)

```swift
import IntrinsicDesign

IntrinsicSpacing.md
IntrinsicRadius.card
IntrinsicColorRole.warning
IntrinsicControlSize.standard
```

Tasteful back-compat: `TastefulSpacing` typealias. Prefer `Intrinsic*` in new code.

Accent on Tasteful iOS: `GlobalAccentColor.shared.currentColor` — not hardcoded hex.

## Web (Tailwind / CSS)

```css
@import "@intrinsic/tokens-css/foundation.css";
@import "@intrinsic/tokens-css/tasteful-app.theme.css";
```

```tsx
className="text-[var(--color-tasteful-muted)]"
className="border-[var(--color-tasteful-line)]"
```

Foundation: `var(--intrinsic-space-md)`, `var(--intrinsic-radius-card)`.

## Themes

| Surface | Theme | CSS prefix |
|---------|-------|------------|
| app.tasteful.to | tasteful-app | `--color-tasteful-*` |
| tasteful.to | tasteful-www | `--color-tasteful-*` |
| Keystone | keystone | `--color-keystone-*` |
| intrinsicvalue.llc | intrinsic-www | `--color-intrinsic-*` |

## Hard bans

- ❌ Raw hex for product semantics in feature code
- ❌ Magic spacing/radius where tokens exist
- ❌ Hand-editing generated CSS or Swift

